title: 11RP for skin?
body: Riot pls, I'm 11RP short for Guardian of The Sands Kha'Zix, would you be dears and give me this RP, I've bought a lot of things if that's good for brownie points? :(

replies.body: No... eleven is too much. This only works for things like one RP off.
the feels, RIOT GIVE THIS DUDE RIOT POINTS!!!
